eSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014043, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 12, "EnglishDescription": "If a child dies in its mother’s womb and were it to remain in the womb it would be dangerous for the mother, it must be taken out in the easiest way possible; and there is no problem if one is compelled to cut it into pieces.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Agar koi bachcha maa ke peyt (stomach) mein mar jaaye aur uska peyt mein rehna maa ki zindagi ke liye khatar-naak ho to chahiye keh usey aasaan tareen tareeqe se baahar nikaale. Chunaan-che agar usey tukde tukde karne par bhi majboor ho to aisa karne mein koi haraj nahi.", "UrduDescription": "اگر کوئی بچہ ماں کے پیٹ میں مر جائے اور اس کا پیٹ میں رہنا ماں کی زندگی کے لئے خطرناک ہو تو چاہئے کہ اسے آسان ترین طریقے سے باہر نکالیں۔ چمانچہ اگر اسے ٹکڑے ٹکڑے کرنے پر بھی مجبور ہوں تو کرنے میں کوئی حرج نہیں۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, 